                                $<%= parseFloat(stats.totalEarnings || 0).toFixed(2) %>
                            </h2>
                        </div>
                        <div class="avatar-sm">
                            <span class="avatar-title bg-soft-light rounded-circle">
                                <i class="bi bi-cash-stack fs-4"></i>
